    "description": "<strong>百看不如一练</strong><br><br>每个关卡都由三部分构成：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876660/extras/17dc8294485874a7dfd300ca3ea5cf21.avif?t=1746448335\" width=616 height=385 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876660/extras/61b65f5e980edc607b83249c7e8bc3d3.avif?t=1746448335\" width=616 height=385 /></span><br>理论: 顾名思义，就是完成该关卡所需的理论知识；<br>练习: 验证所学知识，输入语句，即时得到反馈结果；<br>实战: 运用所学知识，输入代码，控制游戏完成关卡任务；<br><br>理论与实践紧密衔接，帮助您更好地理解编程知识、掌握编程技能。<br><br><br><strong>从玩游戏到做游戏</strong><br><br>教学过程可分为三个阶段：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876660/extras/4e2183862092bcfe21c48190b42f2f7b.avif?t=1746448335\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>基础入门阶段：介绍编程概念，了解代码的构成要素、语法结构，掌握一些基本工具的使用方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876660/extras/b4f9252c30e2634be640d4767e1468c8.avif?t=1746448335\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>应用进阶阶段：通过实际案例，了解如何组织代码，学习简单的算法应用，掌握解决实际问题的思路与方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876660/extras/1d75ff815d61cecd17ff99cd0a7f6fa2.avif?t=1746448335\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>自由发挥阶段：发挥创意，自由编写游戏内容，还能将您的代码分享给其他小伙伴。<br><br>从基础要素到系统应用，循序渐进，降低入门难度。<br><br><br><strong>专为初学者设计</strong><br><br>教学内容通俗易懂、简单实用，教学语言“python”是当前主流编程语言之一，虽然简单易学，功能却很强大，能很快学以致用。",
